<p>This site has been designed to conform to and extensively utilize web standards in order to maximize accessibility, browser compatibility and functionality.
Accordingly this site is best viewed with a browser that properly supports and extensively implements web standards.
This includes most modern web browsers with the exception of Internet Explorer before version 8.</p>

<p>In consideration of the large number of Internet Explorer users, this site has been kludged to provide basic functionality with Internet Explorer 6.</p>
 
